>國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. retweet手足既呢條tweet, 記住comment加#wtsappforhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=34f7687e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&h=44f2ff93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 如果你選擇將10個電話重新打一次出黎，記得加+852<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1. 成本低<br />\n2. 可以迫大家儲下唔同角度文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n1. 本地線唔會要大家post番個舉報cap圖出黎，少左第二次marketing機會 (which is fine)<br />\n2. 外國人參與國際線程度成疑，但我覺得以campaign之名，行宣傳之實。就咁講#chinazi，#culturalrevolution，老實講有d悶。"},{"pid":"f19520288141c9c4fae80f0810badb3c1108e955","tid":1557831,"uid":91842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:14:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c6c20686e655c824ad824202b208f870556ba78","tid":1557831,"uid":91842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:14:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d453cca9679e6f7a102b0efb1ed48a06a03556e","tid":1557831,"uid":260181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:18:18.000Z","msg":"p牌推"},{"pid":"7b319106f895a6cc85c915172e6f87c36254efce","tid":1557831,"uid":58616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfb67ee6509352d9e12396d03391bab9323d82f","tid":1557831,"uid":152966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89f381d43694082f574410877d40af7e681d7614","tid":1557831,"uid":267881,"like":1,"dislik